```plantuml
@startuml Cpanchal1_Chatbot101-with-AWS-Lambda

actor User as "Webex Teams User"
participant "Webex Teams" as Webex
participant "API Gateway" as APIGW
participant "AWS Lambda" as Lambda
participant "icanhazdadjoke API" as JokeAPI

User -> Webex: Mentions bot in room
Webex -> APIGW: Sends webhook event (HTTP POST)
APIGW -> Lambda: Invokes Lambda function
activate Lambda

Lambda -> JokeAPI: GET / (HTTP request)
JokeAPI --> Lambda: Returns joke (JSON response)
Lambda -> Webex: POST /messages (with joke text)
Webex --> Lambda: Message delivery confirmation
Lambda --> APIGW: Returns success response
deactivate Lambda

APIGW --> Webex: HTTP 200 OK
Webex --> User: Displays bot's joke message

@enduml
```